274	## Part 4: Navigation Architecture
275	
276	### Navigator Structure (GoRouter)
277	```
278	ShellRoute (BottomNavigationBar)
279	├── Home (/')
280	├── Browse (/browse)         ← contains Cycle Tracking, Weight & Nutrition
281	├── Library (/library)       ← contains Education, Health Log
282	└── Profile (/profile)      ← contains Settings, Mindfulness
283	```
284	
285	### Bottom Navigation (4 tabs)
286	| Tab | Label | Icon | Route |
287	|---|---|---|---|
288	| Home | Home | `Icons.home_outlined` | `/` |
289	| Browse | Browse | `Icons.search_outlined` | `/browse` |
290	| Library | Library | `Icons.bookmark_outline` | `/library` |
291	| Profile | Profile | `Icons.person_outline` | `/profile` |
292	
293	### Push Routes (detail screens)
294	| Screen | Route | Parent |
295	|---|---|---|
296	| Cycle Tracking | `/cycle-tracking` | Browse tab |
297	| Weight & Nutrition | `/weight-nutrition` | Browse tab |
298	| Pregnancy Progress | `/pregnancy-progress` | Home tab |
299	| Mindfulness | `/mindfulness` | Profile tab |
300	| Health Log | `/health-log` | Library tab |
301	| Mood & Wellness | `/mood-wellness` | Library tab |
302	| Education | `/education` | Library tab |
303	| Article Reader | `/article-reader/:id` | Education |
304	| Settings | `/settings` | Profile tab |
305	
306	### Modal Overlays
307	| Overlay | Route | Type | Parent Screen |
308	|---|---|---|---|
309	| Breathing Exercise | `overlay:breathing-exercise` | full-sheet overlay | Mindfulness |
310	| Stretching Guide | `overlay:stretching-guide` | bottom-sheet | Mindfulness |
311	| Mode Selector | `overlay:mode-selector` | bottom-sheet | Home |
312	| Symptom Detail | `overlay:symptom-detail` | bottom-sheet | Health Log |
313	
314	### Deep Links
315	- `babybump://home` → `/`
316	- `babybump://browse` → `/browse`
317	- `babybump://education/:id` → `/article-reader/:id`
318	- `babybump://settings` → `/settings`
319	
