322	## Part 5: Data Context
323	
324	### Entities
325	
326	| Entity | Key Fields | Provider | Screens |
327	|---|---|---|---|
328	| `PregnancyProfile` | dueDate, lastPeriodDate, currentWeek | `PregnancyProfileProvider` | Home, Pregnancy Progress, Settings |
329	| `CycleEntry` | startDate, endDate, notes, isIrregular | `CycleEntryProvider` | Cycle Tracking |
330	| `WeightEntry` | date, weightKg, note | `WeightEntryProvider` | Weight & Nutrition |
331	| `MoodEntry` | date, moodScore (1-5), note, energyLevel | `MoodEntryProvider` | Home, Mood & Wellness |
332	| `SymptomEntry` | date, symptomType, severity (1-3), notes | `SymptomEntryProvider` | Health Log |
333	| `DoctorVisit` | date, doctorName, notes, nextVisitDate | `DoctorVisitProvider` | Health Log |
334	| `Reminder` | title, date, category, isEnabled | `ReminderProvider` | Health Log |
335	| `SelfCareCheckState` | date, checkedItems: List<String> | `SelfCareCheckStateProvider` | Home, Mindfulness |
336	| `Article` | id, title, topic, content, imageUrl, isBookmarked | `ArticleProvider` | Education, Article Reader |
337	| `UserPreferences` | name, notificationsEnabled, dueDate | `UserPreferencesProvider` | Settings |
338	
339	### Relationships
340	- `PregnancyProfile.currentWeek` drives all week-based content (tips, body changes, nutrition advice)
341	- `MoodEntryProvider` aggregates mood data for `MoodWellnessScreen` trend charts
342	- `SelfCareCheckState` stores today's checklist state, consumed by Home dashboard
343	- `ArticleProvider` tracks bookmarks, consumed by Library tab
